{"tid":266163,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"韓服跑online招人玩呀！包埋教學！","createTime":"2017-06-01T08:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T04:24:57.000Z","uid":58914,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23f7bb571922aab417538b7bba4a4d8cff69d1de","tid":266163,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T08:40:39.000Z","msg":"最近去玩返跑之後去咗韓服覺得幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想招多啲人入黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/5tjXAAygTUYOUdM23\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2F5tjXAAygTUYOUdM23&d=2iDFTzlNQyK5Og%2FdY0fH%2BBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=5104bf16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/5tjXAAygTUYOUdM23</a><br />\n注意！禁止狗公 娘娘 收兵 小圈子行為<br />\n本谷純屬比大家 閒聊 組團 以及入坑教學 既空間<br />\n另外 唔好喺game入面打中文<br />\n我地唔係觀光客 只係一堆偷渡客<br />\n亦都儘量唔好打英文<br />\n<br />\n好啦 正文開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ.點解要去韓服唔去港服？<br />\nA.韓服真係比港服好<span style=\"color: red;\">太</span>多<br />\n<br />\nQ.玩韓服需要準備啲咩？<br />\nA.一個TG<br />\n一個VPN<br />\n一個轉電腦轉韓服地區既心理準備<br />\n以上所講既野谷入面都會教（除咗TG)<br />\n另外仲需要一個有10蚊以上既淘寶帳號黎買ac<br />\n如果唔識我都會儘量教 本身都唔太清楚所以唔好太指望 <br />\n但係都可以用 試玩帳號 既 只係比較多限制<br />\n雖然巴哈都有講韓港差異<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=09426&amp;snA=24024&amp;bpage=1&amp;top=0&amp;ltype=&amp;keyword=對\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D09426%26snA%3D24024%26bpage%3D1%26top%3D0%26ltype%3D%26keyword%3D%E5%B0%8D&d=2iDFTzlNQyK5Og%2FdY0fH%2BBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=434e5747\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=09426&amp;snA=24024&amp;bpage=1&amp;top=0&amp;ltype=&amp;keyword=對</a><br />\n仲有更多優點冇講<br />\n例如全角色TP售賣<br />\n所有服裝相比起港服係超低價<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（一日300TP三十日5000TP)<br />\n而且人數比港服多<br />\n<br />\n大概就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c5f73a89e5f93c501f31b3b7ac4db9a8eb840c","tid":266163,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:26:33.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"7c6ba632179d8bbfbd3d9fcd9267fbced47adc51","tid":266163,"uid":1585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:33:29.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"2dbcb694b36b521c2b04a5ed2961d5fe9b28b833","tid":266163,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:35:08.000Z","msg":"有興趣，但要開住VPN玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a1ab99b5a0249cf1a7fb2f8ffe67ede50f279f","tid":266163,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:36:44.000Z","msg":"會唔會比人屈裝"},{"pid":"916db19d93342d2b4258c50258d2c42a334bd4dd","tid":266163,"uid":36722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"曾經有韓跑ac想down番玩 但唔記得左點down<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85a98428a1406e3d1fa57dac08076e5f4d71f91","tid":266163,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有興趣，但要開住VPN玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要 但係我玩落係差唔多感覺唔到有分別"},{"pid":"8970b69fe3617415aa2c5d1817b27fe3a9f621d1","tid":266163,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會比人屈裝</blockquote><br />\n好難比人屈裝<br />\n因為韓國好多福利<br />\n其中包括超平TP鍊金"},{"pid":"5d24e22953f420fde3f9369c26dda10c08ddb7a7","tid":266163,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經有韓跑ac想down番玩 但唔記得左點down<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWell come"},{"pid":"7c6062470f1ac0ce2e320e80bb526e121702aef4","tid":266163,"uid":4184,"like":0,